---
title: Pan-Seared Scallops & Lemon Butter Sauce with Crème Fraîche Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Broccoli
description: If you think perfectly cooked scallops are only achievable with a dinner reservation at a fancy restaurant, think again! Here, you’ll master the art of the perfect sear, cooking the scallops until they form a beautifully caramelized, golden crust. The garlic-lemon pan sauce that’s drizzled over top is also delicious swiped through bites of crème fraîche mashed potatoes and chili-roasted broccoli. Our compliments to the chef… oh yeah, that’s you!
